
3 user stories about google chrome


1. As a user, I want to group my tabs so that I can organize my browsing sessions efficiently.


Emma is a researcher who works with multiple tabs open at the same time. She finds it difficult to manage them and wants a way to group related tabs for better organization.

2. As a user, I want Chrome to autofill my saved passwords securely so that I can log in faster without compromising security.


John frequently logs into different websites and wants Chrome to remember his passwords. However, he also wants to ensure that his stored credentials are safe from breaches.

3. As a user, I want a built-in screenshot tool in Chrome so that I can quickly capture and save webpage content.


Sophia frequently takes screenshots of online articles for reference. She wants an easy way to capture and annotate images without needing third-party extensions.

